Yes, we’re on lockdown; yes, we’ve been told to stay home to prevent the spread of the coronavirus.
This is what is happening all over the country, thanks to overzealous enforcement of social distancing.
How are these sports not conducive to social distancing?
There is nobody who wants more social distancing than a surfer or a snowboarder.
We’ve got a lot of caged-up people who need freedom to move around, which is possible without violating the social distancing mandate.